rayBuffer</code></a> oder <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>SharedArrayBuffer</code></a>.</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"490\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/dataview-byteoffset.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>dataview</var>.byteOffset</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beschreibung","title":"Beschreibung","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Die <code>byteOffset</code> Eigenschaft ist eine Zugriffseigenschaft, bei der die set Funktion <code>undefined</code> ist. Das bedeutet, dass diese Eigenschaften nur gelesen werden kann. Der Wert der Eigenschaft wird beim erstellen einer <code>DataView</code> bekannt gemacht und kann nicht mehr verändert werden.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"einsatz_der_byteoffset_eigenschaft","title":"Einsatz der <code>byteOffset</code> Eigenschaft","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> buffer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ArrayBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> dataview <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">DataView</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>buffer<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ndataview<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>byteOffset<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 0 (no offset specified)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> dataview2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">DataView</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>buffer<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ndataview2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>byteOffset<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 3 (as specified when constructing the DataView)</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Einsatz der byteOffset Eigenschaft"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-get-dataview.prototype.byteoffset\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'DataView.prototype.byteOffset' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initiale Definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-get-dataview.prototype.byteoffset\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'DataView.prototype.byteOffset' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"br